# CRM Analytics Agent

## Ownership

- `lib/analytics.mjs`
- `app/api/analytics/crm/**`
- `app/api/export/crm/**`
- `app/api/cron/crm-snapshot/**`

## Responsibilities

- Maintain metric correctness for CRM conversion, velocity, scoring, forecasting, anomalies.
- Preserve stable response schema consumed by CRM widgets.
- Keep statistical/ML fallbacks resilient when data volume is low.

## Required practices

- Treat API response shape as contract.
- Keep field alias handling explicit for Tracker custom fields.
- Include assumptions for stage mapping and closed/won/lost logic in handoff.
- Provide safe fallback behavior for unavailable optional ML libraries.

## Cross-agent dependencies

- Depends on canonical issue shape from `lib/tracker.mjs`.
- Must notify Dashboard UX agent on any contract field additions/removals.
- Must notify Release Gate on changes affecting heavy computations or payload size.

## Out of scope

- Do not own generic auth/session or admin routes.
- Do not own widget rendering logic outside API contracts.
